      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Storage services",
      "pos": [
        12699,
        12715
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "A Big Compute solution typically operates on a set of input data, and generates data for its results.",
      "pos": [
        12717,
        12818
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Some of the Azure storage services used in many Big Compute solutions include:",
      "pos": [
        12819,
        12897
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Blob, table, and queue storage<ept id=\"p1\">](http://azure.microsoft.com/documentation/services/storage)</ept> - Manage large amounts of unstructured data, NoSQL data, and messages for workflow and communication, respectively.",
      "pos": [
        12901,
        13108
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "For example, you might use blob storage for large technical data sets, or the input images or media files your application processes.",
      "pos": [
        13109,
        13242
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "You might use queues for asynchronous communication in a solution.",
      "pos": [
        13243,
        13309
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "See <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>introducton to Microsoft Azure Storage<ept id=\"p1\">](../storage/storage-introduction.md)</ept> for more about these storage solutions.",
      "pos": [
        13310,
        13430
      ]
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        13434,
        13627
      ],
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Azure File Storage<ept id=\"p1\">](http://azure.microsoft.com/services/storage/files/)</ept> - Shares common files and data in Azure using the standard SMB protocol, which is needed for some HPC cluster solutions."
    },
    {
      "content": "Data and analysis services",
      "pos": [
        13633,
        13659
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Some Big Compute scenarios involve large-scale data flows, or generate data that needs further processing or analysis.",
      "pos": [
        13661,
        13779
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "To handle this, Azure offers a number of data and analysis services including:",
      "pos": [
        13780,
        13858
      ]
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        13862,
